  "name": {
    "en": "Ayurveda Three Doshas",
    "sa": "त्रिदोष"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": "The three doshas (त्रिदोष - Tri Dosha) are the fundamental bio-energies in Ayurveda: Vata, Pitta, and Kapha. They govern all physiological and psychological functions."
  },
  "members": [
